i have 1 func. name it [牛頓求根法]. to perform. requires 1 num. called [試]. func begin.
    NOTE [[ 設甲為初限，啟算之基 ]]
    has a num 1.0. name it [甲].
    has a num 1.0. name it [乙].
    for [試] times.
        NOTE [[ 求其差謬：乙 = 甲平冪減二 ]]
        mul [甲] <- [甲]. sub its -> 2. prev [乙] topic set its is thus.
        NOTE [[ 求其變率：丙 = 甲倍之 ]]
        mul 2 <- [甲]. name it [丙].
        NOTE [[ 茂 = 乙除以丙 ]]
        div [乙] -> [丙]. name it [茂].
        NOTE [[ 依法損益：甲 = 甲減茂，以逼真值 ]]
        sub [甲] -> [茂]. prev [甲] topic set its is thus.
    end.
    return [甲].
func end for [牛頓求根法] func end.

call [牛頓求根法] <- 1013. print.